description: Returns the enrollment (opt in) status of an account to the Compute Optimizer service. If the account is the management account of an organization, this action also confirms the enrollment status of member accounts of the organization. Use the  GetEnrollmentStatusesForOrganization action to get detailed information about the enrollment status of member accounts of an organization.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The enrollment status of the account.

nested_items.name: statusReason
nested_items.description: The reason for the enrollment status of the account.

nested_items.name: memberAccountsEnrolled
nested_items.description: Confirms the enrollment status of member accounts of the organization, if the account is a management account of an organization.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The Unix epoch timestamp, in seconds, of when the account enrollment status was last updated.

nested_items.name: numberOfMemberAccountsOptedIn
nested_items.description: The count of organization member accounts that are opted in to the service, if your account is an organization management account.
